README.md
     1→# humanize
    12→This modest package contains various common humanization utilities, like turning a
    13→number into a fuzzy human-readable duration ("3 minutes ago") or into a human-readable
    14→size or throughput. It is localized to:
    15→
    16→- Arabic
    17→- Basque
    18→- Bengali
    19→- Brazilian Portuguese
    20→- Catalan
    21→- Danish
    22→- Dutch
    23→- Esperanto
    24→- European Portuguese
    25→- Finnish
    26→- French
    27→- German
    28→- Greek
    29→- Hebrew
    30→- Indonesian
    31→- Italian
    32→- Japanese
    33→- Klingon
    34→- Korean
    35→- Norwegian
    36→- Persian
    37→- Polish
    38→- Russian
    39→- Simplified Chinese
    40→- Slovak
    41→- Slovenian
    42→- Spanish
    43→- Swedish
    44→- Turkish
    45→- Ukrainian
    46→- Uzbek
    47→- Vietnamese
    48→
    49→## API reference
    51→[https://humanize.readthedocs.io](https://humanize.readthedocs.io/)
    52→
